import React from 'react';
import { 
    Box, 
    Grid, 
    FilledInput, 
    Select, 
    MenuItem, 
    Dialog, 
    DialogTitle, 
    DialogContent, 
    DialogActions, 
    makeStyles,
    Typography, 
    Button,
    IconButton,
    CircularProgress
} from '@material-ui/core'
import {Close as CloseIcon} from '@material-ui/icons';

export default props => (
    <Dialog open={Object.keys(props.job).length} fullWidth>
        <DialogTitle>
                <Box display="flex" justifyContent="space-between" alignItems="center">
                    Post Job
                    <IconButton >
                        <CloseIcon/>
                    </IconButton>
                </Box>
            </DialogTitle>

        <DialogContent>
            

        </DialogContent>
        <DialogActions>

        </DialogActions>
    </Dialog>
)
